## Warm Up

Warm Up:3 rounds of: 10 parkour squats/air squats; 10 sit ups; 10 push ups;   10 pull ups OR 10 handstand push ups

## WOD

WOD 10
All levels:
Run a mile OR bike 10 miles OR row 2000 meters

## Cool Down

25 burpees for time.

## Post

Post both times to the comments.

